eu.amidst.core.variables.stateSpaceTypes

Class RealStateSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.variables.StateSpaceType
      • eu.amidst.core.variables.stateSpaceTypes.RealStateSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RealStateSpace
extends StateSpaceType
    This class extends the abstract class StateSpaceType. It defines and handles the state space for continuous variables, i.e., the real state space.
